    <item>
      <title>What I Cant Live Without</title>
      <link>https://prs2rnn.github.io/en/p/what-i-cant-live-without/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 13:08:46 +0500</pubDate>
      <guid>https://prs2rnn.github.io/en/p/what-i-cant-live-without/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;There are 10 things I can&amp;rsquo;t live (I can) without below.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Thermos&lt;/strong&gt; for 1 L. I am fond of tea, so I cannot image a day without it. Having a hot Puer or Ivan-tea nearby, anywhere, in winter or summer, is a pleasure&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Knitted socks&lt;/strong&gt;. Feet need to be warm and if they shiver from the cold at night, it&amp;rsquo;s impossible to sleep. Warm socks help a lot in this situation&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Body Roller&lt;/strong&gt; helps build strong abs and a lower back. Besides it has a small size and is really effective&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hair cutter&lt;/strong&gt;. It&amp;rsquo;s enough for me to cut my hair and shave 1-2 times a week. It is convenient and beneficial&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Crystal deodorant&lt;/strong&gt; after shower prevents bad smells for 24 hours, and it&amp;rsquo;s eco-friendly&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Honey&lt;/strong&gt; is the best thing that nature has created&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nasal irrigator&lt;/strong&gt;. Washing a nose after a day in city environment is a necessity for breathing properly&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Molotov winter jacket&lt;/strong&gt; is the warmest and most comfortable piece of clothing. I can&amp;rsquo;t go anywhere in winter without it&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pepper spray&lt;/strong&gt;. I always carry it in my jacket pocket as a habit so talk to me with respect&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Casio F-91W&lt;/strong&gt;. This watch is on my wrist every day. It&amp;rsquo;s reliable, simple, stylish, and functional. I paid only 15 dollars for it&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;</description>
    </item>
